     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet BehandlingCMMLMDS</b></p><a name=\"BehandlingCMMLMDS\"> </a><a name=\"hcBehandlingCMMLMDS\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/SKS</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-SKS.html#SKS-BOQA\">BOQA</a></td><td>Transfusion</td><td>Behandling med blodtransfusion</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/ATC</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-B03XA01\">B03XA01</a></td><td>Erythropoietin</td><td>B03XA01 - erythropoietin</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L01XX05\">L01XX05</a></td><td>Hydroxycarbamid</td><td>L01XX05 - hydroxycarbamide</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/TreatmentUnspecified</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html#TreatmentUnspecified-demethylating\">demethylating</a></td><td>Demethylerende behandling</td><td>Demethylating treatment / Demethylerende behandling</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentUnspecified.html#TreatmentUnspecified-chemotherapi_aml\">chemotherapi_aml</a></td><td>AML lignende kemoterapi</td><td>AML-like chemotherapy / AML lignende kemoterapi</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Anden behandling</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
